just wanted to share this is how i set up my buttons. These are just the opening tags. IT works too.
<button className="next-btn" onClick={()=>setIndex(prevValue=>{
          return prevValue===people.length-1 ? 0: prevValue+1
        })}>

<button className="prev-btn" onClick={()=>setIndex(prevValue=>{
          return prevValue===0 ? people.length-1: prevValue-1
        })}>

